  "description": "<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p615465/\"><img src=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/2009/images/rss_shuangyu.gif\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a><br /><p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201405/02aa19c82c794734860ed1eb912739e5.jpg\" style=\"height: 452px; width: 280px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\tThis is turning into a roller coaster ride!事态发展如同过山车般急转直下！</p>\n<p>\n\tDespite multiple reports that original Harry Potter stars Daniel Radcliffe, Rupert Grint and Emma Watson would be reuniting in new wizardry footage for a upcoming ride at Universal Studios in Orlando, Radcliffe says otherwise.最近有多则报道称电影《哈利&middot;波特》（Harry Potter）三位主角丹尼尔&middot;雷德克里夫（Daniel Radcliffe）、鲁伯特&middot;格林特（Rupert Grint）和艾玛&middot;沃森（Emma Watson）将在一部新的魔法电影中重聚，影片将在奥兰多环球影城拍摄。不过，丹尼尔的说法却大相径庭。</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;I know nothing about that,&quot; Radcliffe tells the Daily Beast. &quot;They may very well be using existing footage that we'd already filmed for the movies, but I have had no calls or involvement in that.&quot;&ldquo;我对此一无所知&rdquo;。丹尼尔告诉《每日野兽》。&ldquo;他们可能在使用此前我们电影拍摄的剧本，不过我根本就没有参与其中。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tAfter that was cleared up, Radcliffe addressed rumors that he's engaged. &quot;No! Absolute bollocks. Absolute bollocks,&quot; he said.澄清了这则传闻之后，丹尼尔又否认了他订婚的消息。&ldquo;没有！绝对在胡说！&rdquo;他说道。</p>\n<p>\n\tThe actor's denial (about the theme park) comes after Alan Gilmore, art director for the movies and the rides gave MTV News a slightly different account of how the 3-D attraction called Harry Potter and the Escape from Gringotts would look.丹尼尔否认的这则传闻源起电影《哈利&middot;波特和古灵阁逃亡》（Harry Potter and the Escape from Gringotts）的艺术指导艾伦&middot;吉尔莫（Alan Gilmore），他在接受MTV News采访时透露了一些信息，但有人错误地解读了他的话。</p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;It's all new, it's a brand new film,&quot; Gilmore was quoted as saying. When asked if the three original Harry Potter stars would appear in the footage, Gilmore said, &quot;They'll be there! It's quite exciting&hellip;. They're regrouping for one last adventure.&quot;&ldquo;这是一部崭新的电影。&rdquo;这是吉尔莫的说法。当问到霍格沃茨三人组是否会出演时，他说：&ldquo;会的！这太令人兴奋了。他们将为了最后一次冒险重聚。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tThis is how the footage is officially being described &mdash;&quot;Harry, Ron and Hermione break into Gringotts bank to retrieve a magical object that will help defeat Lord Voldemort.&quot; That's according to the Universal Orlando website.根据奥兰多环球影城网站的描述，这部电影的梗概为&ldquo;哈利、罗恩（Ron）和赫敏（Hermione）闯进了古灵阁，寻找一件能帮助他们打败伏地魔的神奇物品。&rdquo;</p>\n<p>\n\tEven if there is no reunion, can't blame us for wishful thinking.这次重聚没机会了，但忠实的粉丝们会一直等下去！</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p615465/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p615465\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615425/\">英国24岁宠物猫获封世界最老 相当人类114岁</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615431/\">脸盲发作：宫崎骏动画中那些撞脸的角色</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615211/\">美国大学生毕业典礼后空翻 出意外笑翻全场</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615456/\">俄19岁男子挑战极限 迪拜高楼顶端玩自拍</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p614542/\">六字英文微小说：言有尽意无穷</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615280/\">不要随便蹭免费WiFi了！小心网银被盗</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p614768/\">20几岁的你需要明白了：生活其实不容易</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615205/\">迪拜遍地豪车遭遗弃 车主负债出逃</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p615236/\">5